  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"g left parenthesis x right parenthesis equals StartFraction x squared minus x minus a Over x cubed minus x minus b EndFraction\"><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>The function <math alttext=\"g\"><mi>g</mi>\n</math> is defined by the given equation, where <math alttext=\"a\"><mi>a</mi>\n</math> and <math alttext=\"b\"><mi>b</mi>\n</math> are constants. In the <em>xy</em>-plane, the graph of <math alttext=\"y equals g left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math> passes through the point <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 0 comma 22 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mn>0</mn><mn>22</mn></mfenced></math>, and&nbsp;<math alttext=\"g left parenthesis negative 22 right parenthesis equals 0\"><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>22</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>. What is the value of <math alttext=\"b\"><mi>b</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
